Songs from Tsongas is the video release of a concert by the progressive rock
group Yes recorded live at the Tsongas Arena in Lowell, Massachusetts, on May
15, 2004. The video features the entire concert performed that night, which
was part of the US leg of the band's 35th anniversary tour.

The setlist features songs from all eras of the band's career, including a
large number of progressive rock classics from their 1970s heyday, as well as

"Mind Drive" from the Keys to Ascension albums (the band had never performed

they played "Children of Light")
